# empty-union-left

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `propagate_empty_relation_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (union ?all (filter (const-bool false) ?left) ?right)
rhs: ?right
